<br>
1) Camp the AC in S Ro. Theres various ideas on how to make it spawn. I only camped it for 3 hours, so I really don't have a clue, cept i killed some crypt mummies + Erg Bluntbruiser and in between SG Hussam spawned and was killed.<br>
The AC is VERY resistant to fire spells. I didn't know that, and only won due to a max-level earth pet and that I had renew elemental memmed. Even though I landed malise, I couldn't land a single Blaze/Cinder bolt. So let your pet and DS do the work. This isn't the fastest way to kill a mob, so if you think someone will KS, just leave right away, cause just about any class can kill the AC faster than a mage.<br>
<br>
2) Get 3250 gp from the bank and go to S karanas. Remember a 10 charge SoW potion, cause Hasten runs FAST and you will most likely be encumbered. ( I weighed about 110/75 with equipment)<br>
<br>
3) At 40 its possible to solo pull shadowed men. I'm not quite sure when you can do it, but make sure to use earth pet cause they flee just as fast as they move. I pulled with Cinder bolt. I killed 6 Shadow men untill I got the Shadowed rapier <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  But I have read it can be a nightmare.<br>
<br>
4) In Rathe Mnt. Hasten have a few placeholders. Maldyn the unkempt, a drake and a SK epic mob. Get a high level to help here if Hasten isn't up. They are on a 17 min. spawn time. Use /ooc to make people hail Hasten and SoW to reach him.<br>
<br>
Good Luck getting your Jboots.<br>
